cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving word representations and proposing a new approach for negative sampling in Word2Vec. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as Word2Vec is a popular model in these fields. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as word representations are important for information retrieval tasks, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as Word2Vec is a neural network-based model.
